race.comment: GEEGEES LEGACY (6) likes to race forward and deserves his win here this grade before getting back from a wide gate when beaten 2.4L in a CL2 at Hobart. He's a solid each-way chance. STREET DIVA (1) resumes and flies fresh and around this circuit. Has won here over the trip and has two trials under the belt. Has a handy 2kg claim and maps for the run of the race. GET 'EM WARRIOR (3) came back to the turf and missed a whisker here this grade/distance. He will push forward and also deserves consideration. ZOETE'S ROCK (2) has been racing on the synthetic and will be better for the first-up outing. He's placed this course/distance and should be around the mark.
